ygData.messageBody:
Bardic Wedding on Xegony
On Sunday, October 31st at 2 . 30 pm Central Time,
Tasher Carbonara (Lv 33 Bard) and Tawney Treewind (Lv 31 Bard)
will be wed in East Karana , along the path leading to High Pass ,
loc - 1862 , - 6030 . After the ceremony , we will proceed to lure some Cyclops
on the valley down the path to have some fun. Free Food and Beer .
The Oligarchia Guild cordially invites all to attend.
Gifts are welcomed but not required. Hope to see you there !

Tasher Lv 33 Bard on Xegony.
